---
title: Spiced Beef Koftas & Garlic Rice with Crumbly Cheese Salad & Mint Yoghurt
description: These koftas are handy parcels of flavour, with tender mince, mild spices and a smattering of currants to add extra sweetness.
Paired with garlic rice, a fresh salad and yoghurt, this is a Middle Eastern feast to remember.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-beef-koftas-garlic-rice-368948c5.jpg
